<br>
Here's a rough version we might try. If we each make up a page we can merge the best ideas together. Let the thinktank commence. I truly believe this idea has great merit. <br>
<br>
****************************************************BAN THE SUN!<br>
<br>
We at GNAW N' PISS (Global Network Against Work and Nuclear Power In Space Society) have long fought against all forms of nuclear power in space, or so we thought. It has recently come to our attention that the sun is in fact a humongous thermonuclear bomb that has been allowed to detonate continuously for over 5 billion years!<br>
Naturally we intend to address this terrible oversight and make certain this terrible menace is ignored no longer. All nuclear power is evil and we therefore propose to ban the sun. Firstly a public awareness campaign has to be organised and this is already underway. The second stage of our plan will involve demonstration marches outside the White House and other centres of Government around the World. A petition form can be found by clicking the link at the end of this page. Please sign it and tell the Government how you feel. <br>
<br>
We are one!<br>
No more Sun!<br>
<br>
We are determined to win this fight. Be assured we will not cave in to Government double talk and questionable scientific reasons for allowing the sun to burn on and bathe this planet in harmful radiation. It states clearly in the 1963 Test Ban Treaty that ALL Nuclear Detonations in Space are ILLEGAL and we will not rest until the Government meets its obligations to enforce said treaty!<br>
Once we have forced the Government to admit its responsibility we will make the following demands guaranteed to rid us of this terrible nuclear threat.<br>
1) We will demand 500 trillion dollars (US) to build a spaceship 50 kilometres in length to reach the sun. Naturally it will run on environmentally friendly solar and wind power generation technologies.<br>
2) We will demand a further 500 trillion dollars (US) to construct a machine designed to extinguish the sun. This will be carried aboard the 'US NO NUKES' Spacecraft to the sun and switched on.<br>
3) We realise that the technologies required to complete items 1 and 2 do not yet exist so we will demand another 1000 trillion dollars (US) to invent them.<br>
4) All such money to be paid into the account of Bruce Ganglion, Secretary, President and Treasurer of GNAW N' PISS.<br>
<br>
Bruce Ganglion.<br>
<br>
<br>
Please Show Your Support For These Other Worthy Causes!<br>
<br>
Ban X RAY DIAGNOSTICS!<br>
Do you realise that this is the number one source of all man made radiation released into the environment?<br>
SHUT DOWN ALL HOSPITALS NOW!!!<br>
<br>
Ban FIRE!<br>
This dangerous power source has caused millions of deaths throughout history. Burned down countless cities and villages. Pushes up insurance rates and is the cause much of our air pollution. Especially since the industrial revolution. <br>
HELP US TO BAN FIRE!!!<br>
<br>
Brought to you by NUCLEARSPACE.NET <br>
<br>
 ****************************************************<br>
<br>
I think we will be ok using GNAW N' PISS as it is slightly different to the other crazier organisation. I've seen stand up comics get away with worse.   <p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
