Adding this:<br>
<br>
Having shared a near death experience our two heroes become the best of friends and decide to work together in the fight against nuclear power. The source of the argument which nearly resulted in their untimely demise.<br>
<br>
Or words to that effect.<br>
<br>
That nasa budget article recieved over 500 replies. Most articles posted get maybe 10! Approval is pending. Let's keep our fingers crossed they publish it. I think humour is the key to advertising. Especially ruthless sarcasm.<br>
<br>
We could build a really convincing site. Perhaps a few slow witted people out there might even think it's genuine rather than a leg pull. There's always a couple. <p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
